Package: perplexicaR
Type: Package
Title: R Client for the Perplexica AI Search API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Felix", "Lennert", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "felix.lennert@icloud.com",
    comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: A client for the Perplexica self-hosted AI search engine.
    Provides Docker lifecycle management so Perplexica can be started from R,
    a batch search helper with checkpoint/resume support, and an ellmer tool
    definition for use in agentic LLM pipelines.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/fellennert/perplexicaR
BugReports: https://github.com/fellennert/perplexicaR/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2
Suggests:
    ellmer,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
